---
// Section 8 - Ultra Protected Modern Version
---

<div id="tp-testimonials-protection" style="background-color: #0c1c2c !important; position: relative !important;">
  <div class="tp-modern-wrap" style="position: relative !important; padding: 100px 0 160px 0 !important; color: #fff !important; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif !important; min-height: 800px !important; overflow: hidden !important; display: block !important;">
    
    <!-- Ultra Protected Background -->
    <div style="position: absolute !important; top: 0 !important; left: 0 !important; width: 100% !important; height: 100% !important; background-image: url('/images/custom-testimonials-bg.png') !important; background-size: cover !important; background-position: center !important; background-attachment: fixed !important; opacity: 0.2 !important; z-index: 1 !important;"></div>
    <div style="position: absolute !important; top: 0 !important; left: 0 !important; width: 100% !important; height: 100% !important; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(14, 55, 107, 0.98) 0%, rgba(10, 20, 38, 0.99) 100%) !important; z-index: 2 !important;"></div>

    <div class="tp-content-safe" style="position: relative !important; z-index: 10 !important; max-width: 1200px !important; margin: 0 auto !important; padding: 0 20px !important; text-align: center !important;">
      
      <!-- Header Area -->
      <div style="margin-bottom: 60px !important;">
        <span style="color: #51acfb !important; text-transform: uppercase !important; letter-spacing: 3px !important; font-size: 13px !important; font-weight: 600 !important; display: block !important; margin-bottom: 15px !important;">A satisfação dos nossos clientes</span>
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif !important; font-size: 52px !important; font-weight: 800 !important; color: #fff !important; margin: 0 0 20px 0 !important; letter-spacing: -2px !important;">O que dizem sobre o nosso <span style="color: #51acfb !important;">serviço</span></h2>
        <div style="width: 80px !important; height: 4px !important; background: #51acfb !important; margin: 0 auto !important; border-radius: 2px !important;"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Slider Container -->
      <div class="tp-slider-safe">
        <div class="tp-slick-final">
          
          <!-- Slide 1 -->
          <div style="padding: 15px !important; outline: none !important;">
            <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06) !important; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1) !important; border-radius: 24px !important; padding: 45px 45px 25px 45px !important; text-align: left !important; min-height: 340px !important; position: relative !important; backdrop-filter: blur(10px) !important;">
              <div style="color: rgba(81, 172, 251, 0.2) !important; font-size: 80px !important; position: absolute !important; top: 20px !important; left: 20px !important; font-family: serif !important; line-height: 1 !important;">“</div>
              <p style="font-size: 18px !important; line-height: 1.7 !important; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9) !important; margin-bottom: 30px !important; font-weight: 300 !important; position: relative !important; z-index: 2 !important;">
                Sempre profissionais, foram os únicos a apresentar um orçamento detalhado. Fiz todas as validações e o resultado final foi excelente. Recomendo o Top Canalizador sem qualquer dúvida!
              </p>
              <div style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1) !important; padding-top: 20px !important; display: flex !important; justify-content: space-between !important; align-items: center !important;">
                <div>
                  <strong style="display: block !important; font-size: 17px !important; color: #fff !important; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif !important;">Paulo Mendes</strong>
                  <span style="color: #51acfb !important; font-size: 12px !important;">Cacém, PT</span>
                </div>
                <div style="color: #ffab00 !important; letter-spacing: 2px !important;">★★★★★</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Slide 2 -->
          <div style="padding: 15px !important; outline: none !important;">
            <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06) !important; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1) !important; border-radius: 24px !important; padding: 45px 45px 25px 45px !important; text-align: left !important; min-height: 340px !important; position: relative !important; backdrop-filter: blur(10px) !important;">
              <div style="color: rgba(81, 172, 251, 0.2) !important; font-size: 80px !important; position: absolute !important; top: 20px !important; left: 20px !important; font-family: serif !important; line-height: 1 !important;">“</div>
              <p style="font-size: 18px !important; line-height: 1.7 !important; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9) !important; margin-bottom: 30px !important; font-weight: 300 !important; position: relative !important; z-index: 2 !important;">
                O serviço foi literalmente TOP! Extremo profissionalismo e transparência no orçamento. Fiquei muito satisfeito com a rapidez da intervenção e a cortesia de toda a equipa.
              </p>
              <div style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1) !important; padding-top: 20px !important; display: flex !important; justify-content: space-between !important; align-items: center !important;">
                <div>
                  <strong style="display: block !important; font-size: 17px !important; color: #fff !important; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif !important;">Sara Oliveira</strong>
                  <span style="color: #51acfb !important; font-size: 12px !important;">Estoril, PT</span>
                </div>
                <div style="color: #ffab00 !important; letter-spacing: 2px !important;">★★★★★</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Slide 3 -->
          <div style="padding: 15px !important; outline: none !important;">
            <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06) !important; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1) !important; border-radius: 24px !important; padding: 45px 45px 25px 45px !important; text-align: left !important; min-height: 340px !important; position: relative !important; backdrop-filter: blur(10px) !important;">
              <div style="color: rgba(81, 172, 251, 0.2) !important; font-size: 80px !important; position: absolute !important; top: 20px !important; left: 20px !important; font-family: serif !important; line-height: 1 !important;">“</div>
              <p style="font-size: 18px !important; line-height: 1.7 !important; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9) !important; margin-bottom: 30px !important; font-weight: 300 !important; position: relative !important; z-index: 2 !important;">
                Finalmente encontrei profissionais de confiança. Foram rápidos a responder e resolveram um problema antigo que ninguém conseguia solucionar. Nota 10!
              </p>
              <div style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1) !important; padding-top: 20px !important; display: flex !important; justify-content: space-between !important; align-items: center !important;">
                <div>
                  <strong style="display: block !important; font-size: 17px !important; color: #fff !important; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif !important;">Armanda Araujo</strong>
                  <span style="color: #51acfb !important; font-size: 12px !important;">Lisboa, PT</span>
                </div>
                <div style="color: #ffab00 !important; letter-spacing: 2px !important;">★★★★★</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
        
        <!-- Controls (Hidden) -->
        <div style="display: none !important;">
          <button class="safe-prev" style="width: 50px !important; height: 50px !important; border-radius: 50% !important; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3) !important; background: transparent !important; color: #fff !important; cursor: pointer !important;">←</button>
          <button class="safe-next" style="width: 50px !important; height: 50px !important; border-radius: 50% !important; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3) !important; background: transparent !important; color: #fff !important; cursor: pointer !important;">→</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style is:global>
  /* Extra override to kill the theme's weird black bubbles */
  #tp-testimonials-protection .slick-track {
    display: flex !important;
  }
  #tp-testimonials-protection .slick-slide > div {
    height: 100% !important;
  }
  /* Force Montserrat availability */
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@800&display=swap');
</style>

<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/slick-carousel/1.8.1/slick.min.css"/>
<script is:inline src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
<script is:inline src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/slick-carousel/1.8.1/slick.min.js"></script>

<script is:inline>
  (function() {
    function initSafeSlider() {
      if (typeof window.jQuery === 'undefined' || typeof window.jQuery.fn.slick === 'undefined') {
        setTimeout(initSafeSlider, 100);
        return;
      }
      const $ = window.jQuery;
      const $slider = $('.tp-slick-final');
      
      if ($slider.hasClass('slick-initialized')) return;

      $slider.slick({
        slidesToShow: 2,
        slidesToScroll: 1,
        autoplay: true,
        autoplaySpeed: 3000,
        arrows: false,
        dots: false,
        infinite: true,
        responsive: [
          { breakpoint: 991, settings: { slidesToShow: 1 } }
        ]
      });

      $('.safe-prev').on('click', function() { $slider.slick('slickPrev'); });
      $('.safe-next').on('click', function() { $slider.slick('slickNext'); });
    }

    initSafeSlider();
    document.addEventListener('astro:after-swap', initSafeSlider);
  })();
</script>
